277,282,291],"tutor_sword-shield":[810]},"species":"tentacruel","gen":"generation-i","leg":false,"myth":false,"baby":false,"eggs":["water3"],"flavor":[{"version":"red","text":"The tentacles are normally kept short. On hunts, they are extended to ensnare and immobilize prey."},{"version":"blue","text":"The tentacles are normally kept short. On hunts, they are extended to ensnare and immobilize prey."},{"version":"yellow","text":"Its 80 tentacles can stretch and contract freely. They wrap around prey and weaken it with poison."},{"version":"gold","text":"Its 80 tentacles absorb water and stretch almost endlessly to CON\u00ad STRICT its prey and enemies."},{"version":"silver","text":"In battle, it extends all 80 of its tentacles to entrap its oppo\u00ad nent inside a poisonous net."},{"version":"crystal","text":"When its 80 feel\u00ad ers absorb water, it stretches to become like a net to entangle its prey."},{"version":"ruby","text":"TENTACRUEL has large red orbs on its head. The orbs glow before lashing the vicinity with a harsh ultrasonic blast. This POK\u00e9MON\u2019s outburst creates rough waves around it."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"TENTACRUEL has tentacles that can be freely elongated and shortened at will. It ensnares prey with its tentacles and weakens the prey by dosing it with a harsh toxin. It can catch up to 80 prey at the same time."},{"version":"emerald","text":"It lives in complex rock formations on the ocean floor and traps prey using its 80 tentacles. Its red orbs glow when it grows excited or agitated."},{"version":"firered","text":"It has 80 tentacles that move about freely. They can sting, causing poisoning and sharp, stabbing pain."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"The tentacles are normally kept short. On hunts, they are extended to ensnare and immobilize prey."},{"version":"diamond","text":"With 80 tentacles for ensnaring victims, it prevents escape until the prey is weakened by poison."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It alerts others to danger by stridently flashing the red orbs on its head."},{"version":"platinum","text":"It extends its 80 tentacles to form an encircling poisonous net that is difficult to escape."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Its 80 tentacles absorb water and stretch almost endlessly to constrict its prey and enemies."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"In battle, it extends all 80 of its tentacles to entrap its opponent inside a poisonous net."},{"version":"black","text":"It extends its 80 tentacles to form an encircling poisonous net that is difficult to escape."},{"version":"white","text":"It extends its 80 tentacles to form an encircling poisonous net that is difficult to escape."},{"version":"black-2","text":"It extends its 80 tentacles to form an encircling poisonous net that is difficult to escape."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It extends its 80 tentacles to form an encircling poisonous net that is difficult to escape."},{"version":"x","text":"The tentacles are normally kept short. On hunts, they are extended to ensnare and immobilize prey."},{"version":"y","text":"It has 80 tentacles that move about freely. They can sting, causing poisoning and sharp, stabbing pain."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Tentacruel has large red orbs on its head. The orbs glow before lashing the vicinity with a harsh ultrasonic blast. This Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s outburst creates rough waves around it."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Tentacruel has tentacles that can be freely elongated and shortened at will. It ensnares prey with its tentacles and weakens the prey by dosing it with a harsh toxin. It can catch up to 80 prey at the same time."},{"version":"sun","text":"Normally, it has 80 poisonous tentacles. The longer one has been alive, the fewer tentacles it will have."},{"version":"moon","text":"Although these Pok\u00e9mon are rare, when a large outbreak of them occurs, all fish Pok\u00e9mon disappear from the surrounding sea."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It fires off ultrasonic waves from its red orbs to weaken its prey, and then it wraps them up in its 80 tentacles."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It communicates with others of its kind by lighting up the red orbs on its head. When the orbs are blinking, it\u2019s a warning sign."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Its 80 tentacles can stretch and contract freely. They wrap around prey and weaken it with poison."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Its 80 tentacles can stretch and contract freely. They wrap around prey and weaken it with poison."},{"version":"sword","text":"When the red orbs on Tentacruel\u2019s head glow brightly, watch out. The Pok\u00e9mon is about to fire off a burst of ultrasonic waves."},{"version":"shield","text":"Its 80 tentacles can stretch and shrink freely. Tentacruel ensnares prey in a net of spread-out tentacles, delivering venomous stings to its catch."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"It has 80 tentacles, each with a venomous tip. These tentacles are also extendible, lengthening when Tentacruel attempts to catch prey. Use caution."}],"evo":{"name":"tentacool","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"tentacruel","level":1,"min_level":30,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/73.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/73.png","capture":60,"happiness":70,"growth":"slow","gender":4,"hatch":20,"ev":{"special_defense":2},"forms":[]}